{"tid":685651,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多人覺得教書就要本身學歷高成績好","createTime":"2018-05-31T14:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T02:59:09.000Z","uid":23423,"like":7,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a0bc7f8d4ab5003dbec7ce160687015ecd979c","tid":685651,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"香港Band 1中學只有俾盡33%<br />\n你話要個Open exam A嘅去教返出個A都有道理<br />\n但根本Band 1尾都已經一年得個一兩個學生有能力拎A<br />\n去到Band 2拎A已經少之又少<br />\nBand 3更加唔使講 百分一都唔知有冇<br />\n係呢到最少佔全港一半嘅學校 教師嘅作用根本就唔係要操班學生拎A <br />\n成日有班人就捉住好多成績差去教師嚟講<br />\n你唔係Band 1根本冇資格要求啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8606b9e982c0dab61bf497d4309693531749ba7","tid":685651,"uid":38904,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"成績好啲就可以搵好啲嘅老師<br />\n<br />\n你依啲思想同支那城市人應該有多啲資源過農村人有乜分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bdf06af1b59a2fa0c2c1abb35dd468e5c33fcf","tid":685651,"uid":135445,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"band 2 3冇資格有好老師？<br />\n你依D咩思想黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de91299f66f75706e1e6234c100e390ef821ba0a","tid":685651,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T21:30:04.000Z","msg":"教師名額&lt; 應徵教師既人<br />\n<br />\n咁咪用成續黎䇴人先囉 有問題咩"},{"pid":"bc785cf155dd8d9463b95360281d3586971e0c23","tid":685651,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:59:55.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩<br />\n咁霆金去教書係咪會出成班霍金?<br />\n讀書講到尾都係靠自己資質"},{"pid":"6bb3d2864a3b3c510326a4a00a94676e5c7e2733","tid":685651,"uid":41619,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T23:02:52.000Z","msg":"Open book exam 同public exam我都聽過<br />\n就係未聽過open exam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s